{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10110748076579-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10110748076579-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000672366","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100142348502-1"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":4,"description":"阅读课内文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":420,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">于是他们日夜赶造巨大的风车和机器，手脚都冻僵了，因为那时候地面上的气候是一天天寒冷。后来工作终于完成了，只等有风，就可以把巨大的风车旋转，轮子和发电机也就可以跟着转动，他们又可以有电力、电光和电热了。可是，一点儿风都没有，不但最小的树叶静静不动，连微细的尘埃也飞不起来。<br style=\"  white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(237, 254, 254);\">　　于是人们又去问气象学家：“请告诉我们，什么时候会再有风？”<br style=\"white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(237, 254, 254);\">　　气象学家深深地叹了口气，整了整他的眼镜，然后说：“没有了太阳，也就没有了风，因为造成风暴的就是太阳。太阳温暖了各地的空气，但是有的地方受阳光多，有的地方受阳光少，所以有的地方比较暖，有的地方比较冷。温暖地方的空气向上升，于是寒冷地方的空气就沿地面流过去补足温暖地方的上升空气。这就形成了风。如果沿地面流动的空气走得太快，这就是风暴；如果它们走得慢一点，那就只成为一种摇曳树枝的轻风。现在太阳既然不再温暖空气，空气就不再流动，你们就白白地建造了这座大风车。”</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>选择。</p><p>人们日夜赶造风车和机器的目的是什么？</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"发展经济。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"用风车发电、照明取暖。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":nu